WEBVTT

00:05:29.880 --> 00:05:32.800
And I thought to myself,
"You want to bet?"

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:38.856
Perhaps my parents could have
found out and could have helped.

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:41.136
But the years of constant caretaking,

00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:44.056
having to wake up
every two hours to turn me,

00:05:44.080 --> 00:05:47.456
combined with them essentially
grieving the loss of their son,

00:05:47.480 --> 00:05:50.816
had taken a toll on my mother and father.

00:05:50.840 --> 00:05:54.416
Following yet another heated argument
between my parents,

00:05:54.440 --> 00:05:57.056
in a moment of despair and desperation,

00:05:57.080 --> 00:06:00.400
my mother turned to me
and told me that I should die.